<br>
All ye flame masters can have your go at this one.<br>
<br>
I had been playing on Sullen since it began and always felt that ganking greens was lame.<br>
I understand arguments for it. I just did not plan on doing it myself. I wanted to fight those "Worthy" opponents.<br>
BUT... I have since changed my outlook.<br>
<br>
So far no one has killed my who was not red.<br>
Due to this fact I am adopting my new PK philosophy.<br>
An eye for an eye, a green for a green.<br>
For every RED con who ganks me one green shall die by my hand.<br>
<br>
TO Elfir:<br>
Your senseless death was brought to you by Skuttles thank her if you wish.<br>
TO Squirrly: Cute name technically I did not PK you since the orcs got the killing blow.<br>
<br>
I still owe three more green deaths to the RED cons who have ganked me so far.<br>
<br>
TO Purity: The fact that you were a red con and killed me on trainer hill will not add to the number or greens that must die. As you were aiding your teammates in an honorable way.<br>
I will only gank back when truly ganked by others.<br>
<br>
You may say its a lame excuse for whoopin on lowbies?<br>
BUT... Dont care tell it to the RED cons who are indirectly responsible for your Deaths.<br>
<br>
Am I whining about the red con gankings I have received?<br>
Maybe, kinda, sorta. BUT at least I am doing something about it. <br>
<br>
